-- Microsoft exploring work force reductions: report
-- 
-- Wed Jan 14, 2009 9:21pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/01/15/us-microsoft-idUSTRE50E0VM20090115

 

 (Reuters) - Microsoft Corp is exploring work force reductions, the Wall Street Journal reported on Wednesday. Highlights: 

 * Jobs cuts could be announced next week-- report says * Cuts likely less than 15,000 rumored; report cites people familiar with plan